paragraphs.text:
%jdbc(hive)

drop table sandbox_datascientist.jfp_anis_2g_only_por_periodo;
CREATE TABLE sandbox_datascientist.jfp_anis_2g_only_por_periodo STORED AS ORC AS

SELECT atp.valor_recurso_primario_cd
, atp.periodo_nr
, xdrm.traf_datos_mb_2g_ca mb_2g
, xdrm.traf_datos_mb_3g_ca mb_3g
, xdrm.traf_datos_mb_4g_ca mb_4g
, cdrm.traf_voz_duracion_2g_ca seg_2g
, cdrm.traf_voz_duracion_3g_ca seg_3g
, voltm.segundos_4g_ca seg_4g
FROM access_data.at_parque_m atp
LEFT JOIN access_data.at_trafico_xdr_m xdrm ON atp.valor_recurso_primario_cd = xdrm.valor_recurso_primario_cd AND atp.periodo_nr = xdrm.periodo_nr
LEFT JOIN access_data.at_trafico_voz_m cdrm ON atp.valor_recurso_primario_cd = cdrm.valor_recurso_primario_cd AND atp.periodo_nr = cdrm.periodo_nr
LEFT JOIN access_data.at_trafico_volte_m voltm ON atp.valor_recurso_primario_cd = voltm.valor_recurso_primario_cd AND atp.periodo_nr = voltm.periodo_nr

WHERE atp.periodo_nr > 202306
-- AND atp.Linea_Negocio_CD = 'WRLS'

AND NVL(xdrm.traf_datos_mb_3g_ca, 0) = 0 AND NVL(xdrm.traf_datos_mb_4g_ca, 0) = 0 AND NVL(cdrm.traf_voz_duracion_3g_ca, 0) = 0 AND NVL(voltm.segundos_4g_ca, 0) = 0
AND (NVL(xdrm.traf_datos_mb_2g_ca, 0) > 0 OR NVL(cdrm.traf_voz_duracion_2g_ca, 0) > 0)

CREATE TABLE sandbox_datascientist.jfp_bandas_no_compatibles_07_mayoritario2
STORED AS ORC
AS

SELECT ani, mes, sitio
FROM (
    SELECT ani, mes, sitio, row_number() OVER(PARTITION BY ani ORDER BY suma DESC) rnk
    FROM (
        -- Subquery 1
        SELECT b.ani, b.sitio, b.mes, b.suma
        FROM (
            SELECT a.ani, a.sitio, a.mes, a.suma, row_number() OVER(PARTITION BY ani ORDER BY suma DESC) rnk 
            FROM (
                -- Your existing subquery logic
                SELECT
                    CASE
                        WHEN SUBSTR(a1.ani,1,3)='549' AND LENGTH(CAST(a1.ani AS STRING))=13 THEN SUBSTR(a1.ani,4,10)
                        WHEN SUBSTR(a1.ani,1,2)='54' AND LENGTH(CAST(a1.ani AS STRING))=12 THEN SUBSTR(a1.ani,3,10)
                        ELSE a1.ani
                    END AS ani,
                    sitio,
                    SUM(duration) suma,
                    SUBSTR(fecha,0,6) mes
                FROM trafico.xdr_enriquecido a1
                WHERE fecha BETWEEN 20231001 AND 20231031 
                GROUP BY
                    CASE
                        WHEN SUBSTR(a1.ani,1,3)='549' AND LENGTH(CAST(a1.ani AS STRING))=13 THEN SUBSTR(a1.ani,4,10)
                        WHEN SUBSTR(a1.ani,1,2)='54' AND LENGTH(CAST(a1.ani AS STRING))=12 THEN SUBSTR(a1.ani,3,10)
                        ELSE a1.ani
                    END,
                    sitio,
                    SUBSTR(fecha,0,6)
            ) a
        ) b
        WHERE b.rnk = 1

        -- Union with Subquery 2
        UNION

        -- Subquery 2
        SELECT c.ani, c.sitio, c.mes, c.DURACION_SEG suma
        FROM (
            SELECT b.ani, b.sitio, b.mes, b.DURACION_SEG, row_number() OVER(PARTITION BY b.ani ORDER BY b.duracion_seg DESC) rnk
            FROM (
                SELECT a2.ani, red.sitio, a2.mes, sum(a2.DURACION_SEG) DURACION_SEG
                FROM (
                    SELECT

                            WHEN substr(a.el_calling_number,1,3)='549' and length(cast(a.el_calling_number as string))=13 then substr(a.el_calling_number,4,10)
                            WHEN substr(a.el_calling_number,1,2)='54' and length(cast(a.el_calling_number as string))=12 then substr(a.el_calling_number,3,10)
                            else a.el_calling_number 
                        end as ani,
                        el_cell_id,
                        fecha,
                        substr(fecha,0,6) mes,
                        sum(cast(substr(chargeableduration,1,3) as int) * 3600 + cast(substr(chargeableduration,4,3) as int) * 60 + cast(substr(chargeableduration,7,3) as int)) DURACION_SEG
                    
                    FROM trafico.comptel_cdr_final a
                    WHERE fecha between 20231001 AND 20231031
                        and el_record_type IN ('GSM_MOC','GSM2_MOC')
                        and callposition=3
                    group by 
                        case when substr(a.el_calling_number,1,3)='549' and length(cast(a.el_calling_number as string))=13 then substr(a.el_calling_number,4,10)
                            when substr(a.el_calling_number,1,2)='54' and length(cast(a.el_calling_number as string))=12 then substr(a.el_calling_number,3,10)
                            else a.el_calling_number

                        el_cell_id,
                        fecha,
                        substr(fecha,0,6)

                            when substr(a.el_called_number,1,2)='54' and length(cast(a.el_called_number as string))=12 then substr(a.el_called_number,3,10) 
                            else a.el_called_number

                        substr(fecha,0,6) mes,

                    FROM trafico.comptel_cdr_final a
                    where fecha between 20231001 AND 20231031
                        and el_record_type IN ('GSM_MTC')
                        and callposition=3
                    group by 
                        case 
                            when substr(a.el_called_number,1,3)='549' and length(cast(a.el_called_number as string))=13 then substr(a.el_called_number,4,10) 
                            when substr(a.el_called_number,1,2)='54' and length(cast(a.el_called_number as string))=12 then substr(a.el_called_number,3,10) 
                            else a.el_called_number 
                        end,
                        el_cell_id,
                        fecha,
                        substr(fecha,0,6)
                    ) a2
                LEFT JOIN tableros.listado_celdas_sectores red ON a2.el_cell_id = red.id_celda AND red.fecha = a2.fecha and red.estado='Comercial'
                GROUP BY a2.ani, red.sitio, a2.mes
            ) b
        ) c
        WHERE c.rnk = 1
    ) x
    WHERE sitio IS NOT NULL
) y
WHERE rnk = 1;

%jdbc(hive)

/* Trafico de datos Up&Down de los clientes del parque en las celdas 2G */ 

DROP TABLE  sandbox_datascientist.jfp_apagado_2G_V2_I1_A;
CREATE TABLE sandbox_datascientist.jfp_apagado_2G_V2_I1_A stored as ORC as

SELECT case when substr(a.ani,1,3)='549' and length(cast(a.ani as string))=13 then substr(a.ani,4,10)
            when substr(a.ani,1,2)='54' and length(cast(a.ani as string))=12 then substr(a.ani,3,10)
            else a.ani end as ani,
        a.cell_id, 
        SUM(a.up) AS up, 
        SUM(a.down) AS down, 
        SUM(a.kb) AS b,
        b.m2m_fl,
        b.tipo_cliente_de
FROM trafico.comptel_xdr_consolidado a
inner join (SELECT valor_recurso_primario_cd, m2m_fl, tipo_cliente_de 
                            FROM access_data.at_parque_m 
                            WHERE Linea_Negocio_CD = 'WRLS' AND periodo_nr=date_format(add_months(current_date,-1),'yyyyMM')) b on substring(a.ani,3,10)=b.valor_recurso_primario_cd
inner join  ELEMENTOS_RED.TABLON_LISTADO_SECTORES c on a.cell_id=c.id_celda and c.data_date=date_format(date_sub(current_date,day(current_date)),'yyyyMMdd') and c.tecnologia='2G'

WHERE fecha BETWEEN date_format(add_months(current_date,-1),'yyyyMM01') and date_format(add_months(current_date,-1),'yyyyMM16')
AND a.cell_id is not null
and substring(c.cluster_nombre,0,2) in ('AN','AS','AO') 
GROUP BY case when substr(a.ani,1,3)='549' and length(cast(a.ani as string))=13 then substr(a.ani,4,10)
            when substr(a.ani,1,2)='54' and length(cast(a.ani as string))=12 then substr(a.ani,3,10)
            else a.ani end, a.cell_id, b.m2m_fl, b.tipo_cliente_de;
            
DROP TABLE  sandbox_datascientist.jfp_apagado_2G_V2_I1_B;
CREATE TABLE sandbox_datascientist.jfp_apagado_2G_V2_I1_B stored as ORC as

SELECT case when substr(a.ani,1,3)='549' and length(cast(a.ani as string))=13 then substr(a.ani,4,10)
            when substr(a.ani,1,2)='54' and length(cast(a.ani as string))=12 then substr(a.ani,3,10)
            else a.ani end as ani,
        a.cell_id, 
        SUM(a.up) AS up, 
        SUM(a.down) AS down, 
        SUM(a.kb) AS b,
        b.m2m_fl,
        b.tipo_cliente_de
FROM trafico.comptel_xdr_consolidado a --ver si combiene más usar trafico.xdr_enriquecido
inner join (SELECT valor_recurso_primario_cd, m2m_fl, tipo_cliente_de 
                            FROM access_data.at_parque_m 
                            WHERE Linea_Negocio_CD = 'WRLS' AND periodo_nr=date_format(add_months(current_date,-1),'yyyyMM')) b on substring(a.ani,3,10)=b.valor_recurso_primario_cd
inner join  ELEMENTOS_RED.TABLON_LISTADO_SECTORES c on a.cell_id=c.id_celda and c.data_date=date_format(date_sub(current_date,day(current_date)),'yyyyMMdd') and c.tecnologia='2G'

WHERE fecha between date_format(add_months(current_date,-1),'yyyyMM16') and date_format(date_sub(current_date,day(current_date)),'yyyyMMdd')
AND a.cell_id is not null
and substring(c.cluster_nombre,0,2) in ('AN','AS','AO') 
GROUP BY case when substr(a.ani,1,3)='549' and length(cast(a.ani as string))=13 then substr(a.ani,4,10)
            when substr(a.ani,1,2)='54' and length(cast(a.ani as string))=12 then substr(a.ani,3,10)
            else a.ani end, a.cell_id, b.m2m_fl, b.tipo_cliente_de;

drop table sandbox_datascientist.jfp_apagado_2G_V2_I1;
create table sandbox_datascientist.jfp_apagado_2G_V2_I1 stored as orc as

select a.ani, a.cell_id, a.m2m_fl, a.tipo_cliente_de, SUM(a.up) AS up, SUM(a.down) AS down, SUM(a.b) AS b
from (select ani, cell_id, m2m_fl, tipo_cliente_de, up, down, b from sandbox_datascientist.jfp_apagado_2G_V2_I1_A
        union all 
        select ani, cell_id, m2m_fl, tipo_cliente_de, up, down, b from sandbox_datascientist.jfp_apagado_2G_V2_I1_B) a
group by a.ani, a.cell_id, a.m2m_fl, a.tipo_cliente_de
;

paragraphs.title: Tabla de agrupado por Celda de datos
paragraphs.text:
%jdbc(hive)

/* Trafico de datos agrupado por celda, clasificado en B2C, B2b, M2M de los Only 2g. Parque de clientes de los only 2g clasif en b2c, b2b y m2m. Trafico en MB de los que tienen consumo mixto */

DROP TABLE  sandbox_datascientist.jfp_apagado_2G_V2_I2;
CREATE TABLE sandbox_datascientist.jfp_apagado_2G_V2_I2 stored as ORC as

SELECT a.cell_id,

        SUM(case when d.ani is not null then b else 0 end)/1024/1024 Mb_cell,
        SUM(case when tipo_cliente_de ='Individuo' AND d.ani is not null then b  else 0 end)/1024/1024 Mb_b2c,
        SUM(case when tipo_cliente_de <>'Individuo' AND d.ani is not null then b else 0 end)/1024/1024 Mb_b2b,
        SUM(case when m2m_fl=1 AND d.ani is not null then b else 0 end)/1024/1024 Mb_m2m,
        
        COUNT( DISTINCT case when d.ani is not null then a.ani else NULL end) Q_usuarios,
        COUNT( DISTINCT case when tipo_cliente_de ='Individuo' AND d.ani is not null then a.ani else null end) Q_b2c,
        COUNT( DISTINCT case when tipo_cliente_de <>'Individuo' AND d.ani is not null then a.ani else null end) Q_b2b,
        COUNT( DISTINCT case when m2m_fl=1 AND d.ani is not null then a.ani else null end) Q_m2m,
        
        SUM ( case when mb_2g>0 AND mb_3g>0 AND mb_4g=0 THEN b ELSE 0 END)/1024/1024 UE_3g,
        SUM ( case when mb_2g>0 AND mb_4g>0 and c.ani is NULL THEN b ELSE 0 END)/1024/1024 UE_4g_sin_volte,
        SUM ( case when mb_2g>0 AND mb_4g>0 and c.ani is not NULL THEN b ELSE 0 END)/1024/1024 UE_4g_con_volte
        
       
FROM sandbox_datascientist.jfp_apagado_2G_V2_I1 a
LEFT JOIN (SELECT case when substr(a.ani,1,3)='549' and length(cast(a.ani as string))=13 then substr(a.ani,4,10) when substr(a.ani,1,2)='54' and length(cast(a.ani as string))=12 then substr(a.ani,3,10) else a.ani end as ani, mb_2g, mb_3g, mb_4g FROM ANALYTICS.off_xdr_mes_5_out_modoff a WHERE aniomes=date_format(add_months(current_date,-1),'yyyyMM') and (a.mb_2g<>0 OR a.mb_3g<>0 OR a.mb_4g<>0) group by case when substr(a.ani,1,3)='549' and length(cast(a.ani as string))=13 then substr(a.ani,4,10) when substr(a.ani,1,2)='54' and length(cast(a.ani as string))=12 then substr(a.ani,3,10) else a.ani end, mb_2g, mb_3g, mb_4g) b ON a.ani =b.ani
LEFT JOIN (select   case when substr(msisdn,1,3)='549' and length(cast(msisdn as string))=13 then substr(msisdn,4,10) when substr(msisdn,1,2)='54' and length(cast(msisdn as string))=12 then substr(msisdn,3,10) else msisdn end ani from elementos_red.hlr_servicios_abonados  WHERE fecha_foto_id=date_format(date_sub(current_date,day(current_date)),'yyyyMMdd')  and ue_srvcc_capability = 1 and substring(imsi,8,2) NOT IN(11,22) and substring(imsi,4,2) = '07' group by case when substr(msisdn,1,3)='549' and length(cast(msisdn as string))=13 then substr(msisdn,4,10) when substr(msisdn,1,2)='54' and length(cast(msisdn as string))=12 then substr(msisdn,3,10) else msisdn end) c on c.ani=a.ani 
LEFT JOIN (SELECT valor_recurso_primario_cd ani from sandbox_datascientist.jfp_anis_2g_only_por_periodo where periodo_nr=202308) d ON d.ani=a.ani

GROUP BY a.cell_id;

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

-- Lo de arriba + la descripcion de la Celda.Hoja de salida de Datos

DROP TABLE  sandbox_datascientist.jfp_apagado_2G_V2_I3;
CREATE TABLE sandbox_datascientist.jfp_apagado_2G_V2_I3 stored as ORC as

SELECT  a.cell_id,
        b.sitio,
        b.region,
        b.provincia,
        b.localidad,
        b.cluster_nombre,
        round(mb_cell,2) Mb_cell,
        round(mb_b2c,2) Mb_b2c,
        round(mb_b2b,2) Mb_b2b,
        round(mb_m2m,2) Mb_m2m,
        Q_usuarios,
        Q_b2c,
        Q_b2b,
        Q_m2m,
        round(UE_3g,4) UE_3g,
        round(UE_4g_sin_volte,4) UE_4g_sin_volte,
        round(UE_4g_con_volte,4) UE_4g_con_volte

FROM sandbox_datascientist.jfp_apagado_2G_V2_I2 a
INNER JOIN  (SELECT id_celda, sitio, provincia, localidad, region, cluster_nombre
             FROM elementos_red.tablon_listado_sectores 
             WHERE data_date = date_format(date_sub(current_date,day(current_date)),'yyyyMMdd') and cluster_nombre<> 'No Aplica'
             GROUP BY id_celda, provincia, localidad, region, cluster_nombre,sitio
            )b ON a.cell_id=b.id_celda ;

%jdbc(hive)

/* Esta query sirve para identificar el perfil de consumo de voz de cada cliente */

drop table sandbox_datascientist.jfp_A2G_voz_total_i0;
CREATE TABLE sandbox_datascientist.jfp_A2G_voz_total_i0 STORED AS ORC AS

select a.ani

, sum(traf_voz_duracion_2g_ca) traf_voz_duracion_2g_ca
, sum(traf_voz_duracion_3g_ca) traf_voz_duracion_3g_ca
, sum(segundos_4g_ca) traf_voz_duracion_volte_ca

, case when d.ani is not null then 1 else 0 end as fl_only_2g_voz
, case when sum(traf_voz_duracion_2g_ca)>0 and sum(traf_voz_duracion_3g_ca)>0 and sum(segundos_4g_ca)=0 then 1 else 0 end as fl_3g_voz
, case when sum(traf_voz_duracion_2g_ca)>0 and sum(segundos_4g_ca)>0 then 1 else 0 end as fl_4g_voz
, case when c.ani is not null then 1 else 0 end as fl_volte_ready_voz


from 
    (select valor_recurso_primario_cd ani, traf_voz_duracion_2g_ca, traf_voz_duracion_3g_ca, 0 segundos_4g_ca
        from access_data.at_trafico_voz_m a where a.periodo_nr=date_format(add_months(current_date,-1),'yyyyMM')
            union all 
    select valor_recurso_primario_cd ani, 0 traf_voz_duracion_2g_ca, 0 traf_voz_duracion_3g_ca, segundos_4g_ca
        from access_data.at_trafico_volte_m b where b.periodo_nr=date_format(add_months(current_date,-1),'yyyyMM')
    ) a
    
left join (select   (msisdn - 540000000000) ani  from elementos_red.hlr_servicios_abonados  
            WHERE fecha_foto_id between date_format(add_months(current_date,-1),'yyyyMM01') and date_format(date_sub(current_date,day(current_date)),'yyyyMMdd')  and ue_srvcc_capability = 1 and substring(imsi,8,2) NOT IN(11,22) --0800 
            and substring(imsi,4,2) = '07' group by (msisdn - 540000000000)
            ) c on a.ani=c.ani
left join (select valor_recurso_primario_cd ani from sandbox_datascientist.jfp_anis_2g_only_por_periodo where periodo_nr= date_format(add_months(current_date,-1),'yyyyMM') ) d on a.ani=d.ani

group by a.ani
, case when c.ani is not null then 1 else 0 end,
case when d.ani is not null then 1 else 0 end;

%jdbc(hive)


---------- Aca estan las llamadas salientes de cada Ani en celda que son 2g

drop table sandbox_datascientist.jfp_A2G_voz_i0;
CREATE TABLE sandbox_datascientist.jfp_A2G_voz_i0 STORED AS ORC AS
SELECT
a.el_record_type RECORD_TYPE
, a.el_cell_id cell_id
, case when substr(a.el_calling_number,1,3)='549' and length(cast(a.el_calling_number as string))=13 then substr(a.el_calling_number,4,10)
    when substr(a.el_calling_number,1,2)='54' and length(cast(a.el_calling_number as string))=12 then substr(a.el_calling_number,3,10)
    else a.el_calling_number end as ani
, 'SALIENTE' tipo
, sum(cast(substr(chargeableduration,1,3) as int) * 3600 + cast(substr(chargeableduration,4,3) as int) * 60 +
cast(substr(chargeableduration,7,3) as int)) DURACION_SEG
FROM trafico.comptel_cdr_final a
where (a.fecha>=date_format(add_months(current_date,-1),'yyyyMM01') and a.fecha<=date_format(date_sub(current_date,day(current_date)),'yyyyMMdd'))
and el_record_type IN ('GSM_MOC','GSM2_MOC')
and callposition=3
and el_cell_id in (SELECT id_celda 
                  FROM ELEMENTOS_RED.TABLON_LISTADO_SECTORES a 
                  WHERE data_date=date_format(date_sub(current_date,day(current_date)),'yyyyMMdd') and tecnologia='2G'
                  GROUP BY id_celda
                  )
group by 1,2,3,4
;

, case when substr(a.el_called_number,1,3)='549' and length(cast(a.el_called_number as string))=13 then substr(a.el_called_number,4,10) when substr(a.el_called_number,1,2)='54' and length(cast(a.el_called_number as string))=12 then substr(a.el_called_number,3,10) else a.el_called_number end ani
, 'ENTRANTE' tipo

cast(substr(chargeableduration,7,3) as int)) DURACION_SEG
FROM trafico.comptel_cdr_final a
where (a.fecha>=date_format(add_months(current_date,-1),'yyyyMM01') and a.fecha<=date_format(date_sub(current_date,day(current_date)),'yyyyMMdd'))

and el_record_type IN ('GSM_MTC')
and callposition=3

drop table sandbox_datascientist.jfp_agrupado_clientes_i1;
create table sandbox_datascientist.jfp_agrupado_clientes_i1 stored as orc as

SELECT  a.valor_recurso_primario_cd ani,
        a.tac_nr,
        g.tac_xdr,
        CASE WHEN a.tipo_cliente_de = 'Individuo' THEN 'Individuo' ELSE 'Empresa' END as  parque_tipo,
        d.sitio sitio_mayor,
        e.tech_sitio,
        e.cluster_nombre cluster_mayor,
        e.provincia provincia_mayor,
        e.region,
        a.m2m_fl,
        h.tecnologia_tx,
        a.sim_lte_fl,
        b.mb_2g,
        c.min_2g,
        a.estado_suscripcion_de estado,
        CASE WHEN a.tipo_cliente_de = 'Individuo' THEN 'B2C' ELSE 'B2B' END as segmento,
        case when f.terminal in ('4G READY' ,'NI_4G') then '4G_READY'
            when f.terminal ='4G SIN LTE' then 'Mala configuracion'
            when f.terminal ='4G SIN USIM' then 'Sin Usim'
            when f.terminal in('NO IDENTIFICADO','ROAMERS','RESTO') then 'Otros' else f.terminal end fl_terminal,
        case when substring(g.imsi,8,1) = '9' and f.mb_4g = 0 then 1 else 0 end sim_lte_xdr_fl,
        case when e.tech_sitio='2G' and h.tecnologia_tx in ('4G','3G') then 'Cobertura 2g - Termianl 3g o 4g'
            when e.tech_sitio='2G' and h.tecnologia_tx is null then 'Cobertura 2G - S/D tecn terminal'
            when e.tech_sitio='2G' and h.tecnologia_tx in ('2G') then 'Cobertura 2g - Terminal 2g only'
            when e.tech_sitio in ('2G/3G','2G/4G','3G/4G','2G/3G/4G') and h.tecnologia_tx is null then 'Cobertura 3g/4g - S/D tecn terminal'
            when e.tech_sitio in ('2G/3G','2G/4G','3G/4G','2G/3G/4G') and h.tecnologia_tx='2G' then 'Cobertura 3g/4g - Terminal 2g only'
            when e.tech_sitio in ('2G/3G','2G/4G','3G/4G','2G/3G/4G') and h.tecnologia_tx in ('4G','3G') then 'Cobertura 3g/4g - Terminal 3g/4g mal configurado'
            else null end as escalera,
        case when e.corredor_nombre like 'SUBTE%' then 1 else 0 end fl_subte

FROM access_data.at_parque_m a
LEFT JOIN (SELECT ani, SUM(b)/1024/1024 mb_2g FROM sandbox_datascientist.ep_apagado_2G_V2_I1 GROUP BY ani)b ON a.valor_recurso_primario_cd =b.ani
LEFT JOIn (SELECT  ani, SUM(duracion_seg)/60 min_2g FROM sandbox_datascientist.ep_A2G_voz_i2 GROUP BY ani)c ON a.valor_recurso_primario_cd =c.ani
LEFT join (SELECT ani, min(sitio) sitio FROM sandbox_datascientist.jfp_bandas_no_compatibles_07_mayoritario GROUP BY ani) d on a.valor_recurso_primario_cd=d.ani
LEFT JOIN  (SELECT sitio, provincia, localidad, region,corredor_nombre, MAX(cluster_nombre) cluster_nombre, tech_sitio
             FROM elementos_red.tablon_listado_sectores 
             WHERE data_date = 20230228 and cluster_nombre<> 'No Aplica'
             GROUP BY provincia, localidad, region, sitio, tech_sitio, corredor_nombre) e  ON d.sitio = e.sitio
left join (select *, case when substr(ani,1,3)='549' and length(cast(ani as string))=13 then substr(ani,4,10) when substr(ani,1,2)='54' and length(cast(ani as string))=12 then substr(ani,3,10) else ani end as ani2 ANALYTICS.off_xdr_mes_5_out_modoff) f on a.valor_recurso_primario_cd=f.ani2 and a.periodo_nr=f.aniomes
left join sandbox_datascientist.jfp_agrupado_clientes_i0 g on a.valor_recurso_primario_cd=substring(g.ani,3,10)
left join access_data.at_tacs_gsma_m h on g.tac_xdr=h.tac_nr and h.periodo_nr=a.periodo_nr
WHERE a.Linea_Negocio_CD = 'WRLS' AND a.periodo_nr=202302
AND a.valor_recurso_primario_cd in (SELECT ani from sandbox_datascientist.ep_A2G_anis2gonly_i4);

DROP TABLE  sandbox_datascientist.jfp_20230320_i1;

SELECT case when substr(a.ani,1,3)='549' and length(cast(a.ani as string))=13 then substr(a.ani,4,10) when substr(a.ani,1,2)='54' and length(cast(a.ani as string))=12 then substr(a.ani,3,10)       else a.ani end as ani,
    a.cell_id, 
    SUM(a.up) AS up, 
    SUM(a.down) AS down,

    , c.corredor_nombre

inner join  ELEMENTOS_RED.TABLON_LISTADO_SECTORES c on a.cell_id=c.id_celda and c.data_date=a.fecha and c.corredor_tipo= 'SUBTE'
WHERE a.fecha >= 20220901
GROUP BY case when substr(a.ani,1,3)='549' and length(cast(a.ani as string))=13 then substr(a.ani,4,10) when substr(a.ani,1,2)='54' and length(cast(a.ani as string))=12 then substr(a.ani,3,10) else a.ani end, a.cell_id, a.fecha, substring(a.imei,0,8), c.tecnologia, c.corredor_nombre;

union
select fecha, ani from sandbox_datascientist.jfp_20230320_i0 group by fecha, ani;

select substr(a.fecha,0,6) mes

    , sum(case when b.tecnologia = '2G' then b.mb else 0 end) as mb_2g
    , sum(case when b.tecnologia = '3G' then b.mb else 0 end) as mb_3g
    , sum(case when b.tecnologia = '4G' then b.mb else 0 end) as mb_4g
    , sum(b.mb) mb_tot

    , sum(case when c.tecnologia = '3G' then c.duracion_hr else 0 end) as duracion_hr_3g
    , sum(c.duracion_hr) duracion_hr_tot

    , e.tipo_cliente_de
    , e.m2m_fl
    , f.fl_only2g
    , d.escalera
    , b.corredor_nombre corredor_nombre_d

left join (select ani, fecha, tecnologia, corredor_nombre, sum(DURACION_SEG)/60/60 duracion_hr from sandbox_datascientist.jfp_20230320_i0 group by ani, fecha, tecnologia, corredor_nombre) c on a.fecha=c.fecha and a.ani=c.ani
left join sandbox_datascientist.jfp_agrupado_clientes_i1 d on a.ani=d.ani
left join (SELECT valor_recurso_primario_cd, m2m_fl, tipo_cliente_de, periodo_nr
                            FROM access_data.at_parque_m 
                            WHERE Linea_Negocio_CD = 'WRLS') e on a.ani=e.valor_recurso_primario_cd and e.periodo_nr=substring(a.fecha,0,6)
left join sandbox_datascientist.ep_A2G_anis2gonly_i4_solapa4 f on a.ani=f.ani and substring(a.fecha,0,6)=f.periodo_nr
group by substr(a.fecha,0,6)
    , e.tipo_cliente_de
    , e.m2m_fl
    , f.fl_only2g
    , d.escalera
    , b.corredor_nombre 
    , c.corredor_nombre 
order by substr(a.fecha,0,6) desc;

--         WHEN SUBSTR(ani, 1, 2) = '54' AND LENGTH(CAST(ani AS STRING)) = 12 THEN SUBSTR(ani, 3, 10)
